      "message": "Addressed the feedback. readErrorBody() now checks the Content-Type header to decide how to parse the error body. If the response is application/x-git, it parses as pkt-line. Otherwise, it first attempts pkt-line parsing (to handle servers that return git protocol errors without the correct Content-Type), and falls back to reading the raw body as plain text. Added a test for the case where the server returns a 403 with a text/plain body.",
